  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a post-apocalyptic world overrun by monsters due to an unknown virus, some people have managed to survive. During these times, an organization formed by elite members of society emerged, fighting against the monsters and aiming to restore the world to its original state. However, this organization is not as benevolent as it seems and employs any means necessary to achieve its goals. For instance, they send ordinary people into monster habitats to retrieve valuable items. If these individuals fail to do so within the allotted time, they are killed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Limbo Inc was founded by influential leaders who, under the guise of restoring order and humanity, assert their power through ruthless methods and the exploitation of survivors. At the heart of the organization is a hidden cult that believes in extracting a mysterious power from the monsters, potentially even curing the infection using this power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to survive by any means necessary!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/2de3f9d2bfc94545a90b51b027bb707e.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a high level of realism, utilizing a minimalist user interface and a dark atmosphere to create a unique sense of immersion. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/84e1326e6bf40e376312893331047a26.poster.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/84e1326e6bf40e376312893331047a26.webm?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/84e1326e6bf40e376312893331047a26.mp4?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/6e50995e3944a52c6fc62df657039c5e.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate abandoned spaces with a team of up to four people. Be cautious: your partners can end up in remote corners of the map, and it's up to each of you to find a way to safety.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/8f9e40436a834035f1cb774baff30bdf.poster.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/8f9e40436a834035f1cb774baff30bdf.webm?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/8f9e40436a834035f1cb774baff30bdf.mp4?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/45370f0f58e45e20fa7f025f0bab9ce0.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore unique levels, with a promise of regular content updates. Each level offers new escape routes and its own unique dangers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/c1589aa87a862fc83d5f421dc1aee91c.poster.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/c1589aa87a862fc83d5f421dc1aee91c.webm?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/c1589aa87a862fc83d5f421dc1aee91c.mp4?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/d9412b83dd8948f95618e04c24a6e8b0.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware: you will be the leader against one of several unique enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/62e2ff5fd10dd751c0d4b598cbcee262.poster.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/62e2ff5fd10dd751c0d4b598cbcee262.webm?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/62e2ff5fd10dd751c0d4b598cbcee262.mp4?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a post-apocalyptic world overrun by monsters due to an unknown virus, some people have managed to survive. During these times, an organization formed by elite members of society emerged, fighting against the monsters and aiming to restore the world to its original state. However, this organization is not as benevolent as it seems and employs any means necessary to achieve its goals. For instance, they send ordinary people into monster habitats to retrieve valuable items. If these individuals fail to do so within the allotted time, they are killed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Limbo Inc was founded by influential leaders who, under the guise of restoring order and humanity, assert their power through ruthless methods and the exploitation of survivors. At the heart of the organization is a hidden cult that believes in extracting a mysterious power from the monsters, potentially even curing the infection using this power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to survive by any means necessary!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/2de3f9d2bfc94545a90b51b027bb707e.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a high level of realism, utilizing a minimalist user interface and a dark atmosphere to create a unique sense of immersion. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/84e1326e6bf40e376312893331047a26.poster.avif?t=1730802898\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960070/extras/84e1326e6bf40e376312893331047a26.webm?t=1730802898\" type=\"video/we